msg: This is an empty revision for padding.

author: sussman
msg: Stop the misleading, alarmist chatter in the apache error log.
("404 could not determine resource kind").  The prep functions were
written before svn_fs_check_path existed, but now we can do better.
* mod_dav_svn/repos.c (dav_svn_prep_regular, dav_svn_prep_working):
simplify -- use svn_fs_check_path, instead of svn_fs_is_dir.

author: sussman
msg: * dav_svn.h, repos.c (dav_svn_resource_kind): rename from
dav_svn_is_new, and rewrite to be simpler: simply return the
appropriate node-kind, depending on the resource.

author: brane
msg: Fix a bug in the predicate logic that caused the wrong convert_error method
to be called when combining different predicates.
* subversion/tests/clients/cmdline/svntest/testcase.py (_Predicate.__init__):
If the parameter is a _Predicate, become that instance instead of just
copying the attributes.
(TestCase.__init__): Because of this change, special magic is no longer
necessary; remove it.
